monstrate the benefits of scale and operating leverage. In contrast, the **AI segment** is in an earlier stage of development; the company expects a multi-year investment horizon of heavy capital expenditures for compute infrastructure before the AI segment translates into sustained positive Segment Adjusted EBITDA.',
